@EU_Commission Effective #uploadfilters are technically not feasible.

Anyone knows how to index all existing copyrighted material to check all uploads within a reasonable time?

Even if it was possible, how can abusive overload of upload filters through bulk copyright claims be prevented?

@EU_Commission "Strengthen the cultural sector"? More like, shut down small businesses for the big ones. Kill off smaller artists. And shut down freedom of speech.

The only winners here are you and your pockets.
EU proven dictatorship.
